1 0 0 1 56 736.0 Tm (recruits aimed at a single coordinate. The vagueness of the dance matches the vagueness of) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 722.0 Tm (the resource it describes.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 708.0 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 56 694.0 Tm (On this reading, asking a dance to be more precise would be a category error. The dance is) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 680.0 Tm (honest about an inherently fuzzy target, and the colony's foraging benefits from a) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 666.0 Tm (controlled spread of search effort rather than a false pinpoint. Imprecision, calibrated to) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 652.0 Tm (the world, is information.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 638.0 Tm () Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 620.0 Tm (Conclusion) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 56 606.0 Tm (Individual waggle dances are imprecise, but the imprecision is matched to the spatial extent) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 592.0 Tm (of real resources and spreads recruits productively across a foraging zone. Robustness to) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 578.0 Tm (signal noise is built into the colony's collective response, and the dance is best judged) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 564.0 Tm (not as a coordinate but as a well-calibrated hint.) Tj
1 0 0 1 56 550.0 Tm () Tj
